00:39:34,360 --> 00:39:36,620
那道划痕 是我在别的地方刮的 我搞错了
I think I mistook a scratch from some other place.

723
00:39:37,200 --> 00:39:38,330
什么
What?

724
00:39:39,910 --> 00:39:41,000
你搞错了？
You were mistaken?

725
00:39:41,080 --> 00:39:44,040
不过不管是不是我搞错了 你们有证据吗
Whether it was a mistake or not, I wonder if there is proof.

726
00:39:45,040 --> 00:39:46,540
我试探了几句
When I raised my voice a little,

727
00:39:46,630 --> 00:39:48,880
金万福那老头就看起来要承认了
that old man seemed to agree with me.

728
00:39:53,260 --> 00:39:54,220
对
You're right.

729
00:39:55,090 --> 00:39:56,680
没有证据
There is no proof.

730
00:39:57,260 --> 00:39:58,390
但是你不应该这样做
But you shouldn't do this.

731
00:39:58,560 --> 00:39:59,890
那你能怎么办呢
But what are you gonna do?

732
00:40:00,140 --> 00:40:02,730
所有人都看到你撞我的车了
Everyone saw you crash the wagon into my car.

733
00:40:07,560 --> 00:40:09,570
该怎么办呢
What should I do about...

734
00:40:09,650 --> 00:40:10,650
抱歉
I'm sorry.

735
00:40:11,150 --> 00:40:13,030
可恶 好
Damn! That's right.

736
00:40:13,110 --> 00:40:13,990
抱歉 我忘了
Sorry, I forgot.

737
00:40:14,280 --> 00:40:16,780
你说过让我和你的律师谈
You told me to talk to your lawyer.

738
00:40:17,570 --> 00:40:19,830
说吧 你打算怎么解决
So tell me, how will you resolve this?

739
00:40:21,490 --> 00:40:22,500
好 那个…
Well...

740
00:40:24,000 --> 00:40:25,790
-那… -你说啊
-So... -So, tell me.

741
00:40:25,870 --> 00:40:27,250
你打算怎么解决
What are you going to do?

742
00:40:27,830 --> 00:40:29,670
好 前…
Yes, M...

743
00:40:30,500 --> 00:40:31,250
好 前…
-M... -Tell me.

744
00:40:31,340 --> 00:40:33,550
-前… -说啊
-M... -Tell me.

745
00:40:33,630 --> 00:40:34,920
你说完 我们再相亲
Tell me what you're going to do.

746
00:40:35,510 --> 00:40:37,470
前…
Mr...

747
00:40:38,970 --> 00:40:41,720
前辈个屁 前辈就该有前辈的样子
Forget that we went to the same school!

748
00:40:41,810 --> 00:40:43,310
别给学校抹黑
You're an embarrassment to our alma mater!

749
00:40:43,390 --> 00:40:46,310
都是因为你污蔑别人刮伤你的车
This whole mess is your fault for falsely accusing someone

750
00:40:46,390 --> 00:40:48,440
才会挑起这场事端 你这家伙
for scratching your car, man!

751
00:40:51,570 --> 00:40:52,650
-该死 -搞什么鬼
-Damn it! -What the heck?

752
00:40:53,030 --> 00:40:54,690
她在说什么 你是我的学妹吗
What is she saying? We went to the same school?

753
00:40:54,780 --> 00:40:57,780
你竟敢那样跟我说话
How dare you talk to me like that?

754
00:40:57,860 --> 00:40:59,030
-喂 -她…是
-Hey! -She is... Yes?

755
00:40:59,530 --> 00:41:01,330
-我要告你们两个 -好
-You two, get ready to be sued. -Yeah.

756
00:41:02,540 --> 00:41:03,830
你们得尝尝被告的滋味
You need to be sued.

757
00:41:04,910 --> 00:41:05,910
千永裴
Mr. Cheon Yeongbae,

758
00:41:06,620 --> 00:41:07,830
你告我们吧
go ahead and sue us.

759
00:41:08,710 --> 00:41:11,710
我的律师有多么厉害
You'll find out how amazing...

760
00:41:12,960 --> 00:41:14,300
你会知道的
my lawyer is.

761
00:41:23,600 --> 00:41:25,810
玛丽 等一下
Mari, wait a minute.

762
00:41:28,560 --> 00:41:32,190
就算你再怎么生气 也不能发这么大火啊 是吧
Even if you were mad, you totally lost your cool.

763
00:41:32,270 --> 00:41:34,570
够了 你来这里干什么
I don't care. Why are you here?

764
00:41:34,650 --> 00:41:37,280
我吗 还能干什么 我和你一样…
Why do you think? Because of the same reason as you--

765
00:41:40,410 --> 00:41:41,490
玛丽
Mari.

766
00:41:42,580 --> 00:41:44,540
你来这里的原因究竟是什么呢
What was the reason you were here for?

767
00:41:46,500 --> 00:41:47,830
千律师说
Mr. Cheon says that

768
00:41:48,410 --> 00:41:53,000
律师要替他的委托人战斗
a lawyer fights in their client's stead.

769
00:41:55,710 --> 00:41:58,090
好 我知道了 如果你处理不了就告诉我
It's okay. Tell me if you can't.

770
00:41:58,170 --> 00:41:59,470
我可以替你解决
I can do it instead.

771
00:42:02,550 --> 00:42:05,720
我也能战斗 我来处理
I can fight too. I'll do it.

772
00:42:15,480 --> 00:42:17,900
来 建宇
All right, Gunwoo.

773
00:42:18,150 --> 00:42:19,700
吃饭吧
Let's eat.

774
00:42:20,660 --> 00:42:21,660
给
Here.

775
00:42:23,410 --> 00:42:24,870
他是坏人吧
Isn't he a bad guy?

776
00:42:24,950 --> 00:42:26,620
爷爷 他欺负你啊
He's giving you a hard time.

777
00:42:30,330 --> 00:42:31,420
没错
Yes.

778
00:42:32,000 --> 00:42:32,920
他是坏人
He's a bad guy.

779
00:42:33,000 --> 00:42:34,460
你好
You're here.

780
00:42:34,540 --> 00:42:35,500
姐姐
Mari.

781
00:42:36,500 --> 00:42:37,550
等一下
Wait.

782
00:42:40,880 --> 00:42:42,390
我想把这个给你
I wanted to give you this.

783
00:42:44,140 --> 00:42:45,010
什么
Excuse me?

784
00:42:45,510 --> 00:42:47,520
我心里实在是过意不去
I don't feel comfortable.

785
00:42:47,770 --> 00:42:50,180
如果我早点赔偿的话 就不会发生这种事了
If I had paid for the damages, things wouldn't have gone this far.

786
00:42:50,770 --> 00:42:52,270
我四处筹到些钱
I got the money from here and there.

787
00:42:52,350 --> 00:42:54,230
虽然不够 但请拿这些钱去解决吧
It's not enough, but resolve it with this money.

788
00:42:56,150 --> 00:42:57,980
姐姐 这是我给你的
Mari. This is from me.

789
00:43:02,910 --> 00:43:03,950
我有这个就够了
This is more than enough.

790
00:43:16,420 --> 00:43:17,880
所有的保安都讨厌他
All of the security guards hate him.

791
00:43:18,630 --> 00:43:21,550
也赔过他不少钱
We ended up paying him a hefty sum as well.

792
00:43:22,800 --> 00:43:25,890
所有人都不愿意来这个岗亭工作
Nobody wants to work here.

793
00:43:26,050 --> 00:43:28,770
所以我这个老头才能在这里工作
That's why an old man like me can work here.

794
00:43:28,850 --> 00:43:31,390
从某个角度来说 也多亏了他
So in some ways, I work here thanks to that person.

795
00:43:31,480 --> 00:43:33,900
你打算一直被他刁难 还要忍着他吗
But you have to put up with so much.

796
00:43:34,060 --> 00:43:36,440
唉唷 赚钱哪有那么容易
Goodness. It's not easy to make money.

797
00:43:36,520 --> 00:43:38,270
这点委屈当然要忍受
That much trouble is expected.

798
00:43:41,650 --> 00:43:43,530
不过我还是挺喜欢这里的
I liked working here.

799
00:43:44,910 --> 00:43:48,030
有很多好人 我也越来越喜欢他们了
There are nice residents here and I grew attached to them.

800
00:43:55,000 --> 00:43:56,290
爷爷
Grandpa!

801
00:43:56,380 --> 00:43:58,590
嗯 建宇
Hey, Gunwoo!

802
00:44:21,320 --> 00:44:22,360
姐姐
Mari!

803
00:44:24,990 --> 00:44:26,780
你不喜欢棒棒糖吗
Don't you like lollipops?

804
00:44:29,120 --> 00:44:30,990
我不是不喜欢
It's not that I don't like them, but...

805
00:44:35,710 --> 00:44:36,620
给你
Here you go.

806
00:44:38,670 --> 00:44:40,210
这也是糖吗
Is this candy too?

807
00:44:40,290 --> 00:44:41,800
这是我喜欢的糖 你尝尝看
It's something I like. Try it.

808
00:44:45,050 --> 00:44:46,630
不过怎么这么贵
Why is it so expensive?

809
00:44:46,970 --> 00:44:50,010
你得尝点好东西 才会萌生想要成功的念头
You need to taste nice things so you get the drive to succeed.

810
00:44:52,060 --> 00:44:53,640
并对你爷爷尽孝
And be good to your grandpa.

811
00:44:53,730 --> 00:44:55,980
我现在才七岁
I'm only seven years old.

812
00:44:57,440 --> 00:44:59,650
成功是没有年龄限制的
There's no age limit to success.

813
00:45:00,570 --> 00:45:02,280
-明白了吧 -明白了
-You got that? -Okay.

814
00:45:03,030 --> 00:45:07,860
不过这笔钱够我和爷爷奶奶 好好吃一顿五花肉了
But with this money, Grandpa, Grandma, and I can have tons of pork belly.

815
00:45:09,870 --> 00:45:12,240
给你 这是牛肉
Here. It's beef.

816
00:45:12,450 --> 00:45:14,620
和爷爷奶奶烤着吃吧
Have it with your grandparents.

817
00:45:14,700 --> 00:45:16,540
我该怎么跟奶奶说呢
What do I tell Grandma?

818
00:45:16,620 --> 00:45:18,330
你就说这是律师姐姐给的
Tell her it's from the lawyer lady.

819
00:45:18,830 --> 00:45:20,250
让她不要担心 振作起来
Tell her not to worry and cheer up.

820
00:45:21,090 --> 00:45:22,250
谢谢你
Thank you.

821
00:45:22,340 --> 00:45:23,300
回去吧
Go home.

822
00:45:27,380 --> 00:45:28,430
姐姐
Mari.

823
00:45:33,100 --> 00:45:34,060
好
Okay.

824
00:45:41,230 --> 00:45:42,520
我要疯了
I'm losing it.

825
00:45:49,910 --> 00:45:51,820
你在智勋的事务所实习？
You're training at Jihun's office?

826
00:45:52,410 --> 00:45:54,160
-是的 -为什么
-Yes. -Why?

827
00:45:56,790 --> 00:45:58,330
我不该问为什么吗
Maybe I shouldn't ask why.

828
00:45:58,920 --> 00:46:01,170
是啊 这主意不错
Either way, it's not a bad idea.

829
00:46:01,250 --> 00:46:04,130
既然要学 跟着智勋学挺好的
It will be good to learn from Jihun.

830
00:46:05,460 --> 00:46:06,420
好像不是这样吧
I don't know about that.

831
00:46:07,380 --> 00:46:10,590
他当检察官的时候也这么鲁莽吗
Was he that reckless as a prosecutor too?

832
00:46:11,300 --> 00:46:12,390
他又闯祸了吗
Did he cause trouble again?

833
00:46:12,470 --> 00:46:14,060
真是一模一样
It's the same.

834
00:46:14,140 --> 00:46:15,850
-一模一样 -什么
-You ask that too. -What's the same?

835
00:46:15,930 --> 00:46:18,180
民赫哥也先问他是不是闯祸了
Minhyeok asked if he caused trouble too.

836
00:46:19,770 --> 00:46:22,810
他检察官时期的故事太多了
There are too many stories about Jihun as a prosecutor.

837
00:46:22,980 --> 00:46:25,480
我以后再告诉你 有趣的事太多了
I'll tell you later. There are some fun stories.

838
00:46:26,780 --> 00:46:29,320
所以他又闯什么祸了
So, what did he do this time?

839
00:46:31,490 --> 00:46:32,450
是这样的
So...

840
00:46:32,950 --> 00:46:35,080
什么 撞别人的车？
What? He crashed into a car?

841
00:46:35,160 --> 00:46:37,450
天啊 确实是他的作风
Wow, that's so like Jihun.

842
00:46:39,210 --> 00:46:40,410
你觉得我能解决吗
Do you think I can resolve it?

843
00:46:41,330 --> 00:46:42,830
先解决撞车的事
Take care of the car damages,

844
00:46:42,920 --> 00:46:44,750
再帮建宇爷爷保住工作
let Gunwoo's grandfather keep his job,

845
00:46:44,920 --> 00:46:47,130
让那家伙不能再欺负他不就行了吗
and stop the guy harassing him. Isn't it all you have to do?

846
00:46:48,300 --> 00:46:49,470
还挺有意思的
That sounds fun.

847
00:46:49,550 --> 00:46:51,300
-前辈 -干吗
-Yejin. -What?

848
00:46:52,930 --> 00:46:54,680
好吧
Okay, fine.

849
00:46:55,100 --> 00:46:57,600
就算我把撞车的事解决了
Let's say I somehow take care of the car damages.

850
00:46:57,850 --> 00:47:01,140
那种人能在一夜之间改变吗 他这辈子都是这么活过来的
But how can he change overnight? He lived like that all his life.

851
00:47:01,640 --> 00:47:03,350
让他重新做人不就行了
Make a new man out of him then.

852
00:47:03,440 --> 00:47:05,770
-什么 -很简单
-What? -It's simple.

853
00:47:06,150 --> 00:47:07,820
千永裴改过自新计划
The Cheon Yeongbae Reform Project.

854
00:47:09,900 --> 00:47:11,030
白玛丽
Baek Mari.

855
00:47:11,570 --> 00:47:14,620
你不要想得太复杂 否则简单的事也会变得复杂
Don't think too hard about it. It only complicates things.

856
00:47:16,740 --> 00:47:18,450
改过自新计划？
A reform project?

857
00:47:23,120 --> 00:47:24,580
千智勋律师 你在哪
ATTORNEY CHEON JIHUN WHERE ARE YOU

858
00:47:48,320 --> 00:47:49,530
你找我干吗
Why did you call me?

859
00:47:50,400 --> 00:47:51,650
你来啦
You're here.

860
00:47:52,320 --> 00:47:55,620
怎么样 你想到解决办法了吗
Have you come up with a solution?

861
00:47:56,200 --> 00:47:57,780
我还在想
I'm still thinking.

862
00:47:58,830 --> 00:48:00,120
你叫我过来就是为了这个吗
Is that why you called me?

863
00:48:03,790 --> 00:48:05,250
事务长说
Mr. Sa told me

864
00:48:05,960 --> 00:48:08,750
到目前为止 你没有一件案件是解决不了的
that there wasn't a single case you weren't able to resolve.

865
00:48:09,880 --> 00:48:12,880
换做你的话 这个案子也能解决吧
You can resolve this case too, right?

866
00:48:12,970 --> 00:48:15,890
当然 不过总听别人夸我 我都听腻了
Yes. But I'm getting tired of the praise.

867
00:48:16,800 --> 00:48:18,510
我现在很认真
I'm being serious.

868
00:48:20,390 --> 00:48:23,730
玛丽 解决事情的方式
Mari, there are many ways

869
00:48:23,810 --> 00:48:26,270
有很多种
to resolve a case.

870
00:48:28,020 --> 00:48:31,440
有些人会用一个简单的道歉
Some people will try to cover it up

871
00:48:32,860 --> 00:48:34,900
来平息事端
with a simple apology.

872
00:48:37,700 --> 00:48:40,370
也有些人只尝试用法律来解决问题
Some people will try to deal with it only using the law.

873
00:48:40,700 --> 00:48:44,540
但来找我们的人并不是来了解法律的
But the people don't come to us to learn about the law.

874
00:48:45,120 --> 00:48:46,870
而是来寻求帮助的
They come because they need help.

875
00:48:50,590 --> 00:48:54,720
与其抱着律师就必须用法律 来解决问题的想法
Instead of thinking that a lawyer must use the law,

876
00:48:55,630 --> 00:48:57,220
我希望你想一想
I want you to think

877
00:48:58,510 --> 00:49:01,810
你能实现的最理想的办法
about the most ideal way that you are comfortable with.

878
00:49:04,100 --> 00:49:05,810
这是我给你的作业
That's my homework for you.

879
00:49:13,610 --> 00:49:14,570
该死
Shoot.

880
00:49:25,790 --> 00:49:28,210
你明白我的意思吧
Did you understand what I meant?

881
00:49:29,750 --> 00:49:30,790
是的
Yes.

882
00:49:34,460 --> 00:49:35,800
律师事务所 二楼
OFFICE OF LAW, 2F

883
00:49:35,880 --> 00:49:37,380
明天见
See you tomorrow.

884
00:49:45,680 --> 00:49:47,440
你来啦
Oh, you're here.

885
00:49:47,520 --> 00:49:49,400
玛丽 你来得真早啊
Mari, you're here early.

886
00:49:49,730 --> 00:49:50,730
早上好
Good morning.

887
00:49:51,810 --> 00:49:53,150
我想到了一个主意
I had an idea.

888
00:49:53,360 --> 00:49:54,190
主意？
An idea?

889
00:49:55,480 --> 00:49:56,780
你找到解决办法了吗
Did you find the solution?

890
00:49:58,070 --> 00:49:59,240
应该是吧
Hmm. Probably.

891
00:49:59,660 --> 00:50:01,240
虽然我不知道这个办法对不对
But I'm not sure if it's the right way.

892
00:50:01,820 --> 00:50:04,240
事务长 你能帮我吗
Mr. Sa, can you help me?

893
00:50:04,330 --> 00:50:05,200
我吗
Me?

894
00:50:13,290 --> 00:50:15,550
毛会长 你这么喜欢玩宾果游戏吗
Chairman, why do you like bingo so much?

895
00:50:15,630 --> 00:50:17,300
我玩这个是因为喜欢吗
I don't play it because I like it.

896
00:50:17,920 --> 00:50:19,510
是你说只有我赢了 你才接我的案子
You said you'd take my case if I beat you.

897
00:50:19,590 --> 00:50:22,260
所以我不是说你当初要活得善良点嘛
I told you to live an honest life to begin with.

898
00:50:22,340 --> 00:50:23,800
我以后会活得很善良
I will from now on.

899
00:50:24,720 --> 00:50:25,810
真的吗
Really?

900
00:50:27,640 --> 00:50:29,770
嗯 你看着吧
Yes. Watch me.

901
00:50:30,850 --> 00:50:32,230
17
Seventeen.

902
00:50:39,900 --> 00:50:42,490
当日

903
00:50:46,120 --> 00:50:47,330
今天就到时间了
Today is D-Day.

904
00:50:48,250 --> 00:50:49,540
你们死定了
They're both dead.

905
00:50:53,670 --> 00:50:56,250
这些人在干吗 发生什么事了吗
What are they doing here? Did something happen?

906
00:50:56,420 --> 00:50:57,460
千永裴专务
Mr. Cheon Yeongbae!

907
00:50:58,670 --> 00:51:00,050
有人向电视台爆料
Someone gave the station a tip.

908
00:51:00,720 --> 00:51:01,550
爆料？
A tip?

909
00:51:01,630 --> 00:51:03,470
-你怎么会这样做 -这是真的吗
-How could you do it? -Is it true?

910
00:51:03,550 --> 00:51:05,510
-这些家伙… -请说句话
