918
00:51:23,910 --> 00:51:26,620
我们的社会还是很美好的嘛
Our society is still a good place to live...

919
00:51:27,030 --> 00:51:28,240
你们来采访什么
What are you here for again?

920
00:51:29,120 --> 00:51:31,120
天气真好
The weather is so nice.

921
00:51:31,210 --> 00:51:34,830
最近社区居民 刁难保安的事件层出不穷
In recent days, we keep hearing about the residents abusing security guards.

922
