-I hope I did the right thing. -Of course, you did.

932
00:52:00,110 --> 00:52:02,110
千永裴先生平时为人如何
What is Mr. Cheon Yeongbae like?

933
00:52:02,190 --> 00:52:03,240
那个 他…
Well, he is...

934
00:52:03,360 --> 00:52:04,160
姐姐
Mari!

935
00:52:04,950 --> 00:52:06,370
而且他…
And he is...

936
00:52:06,450 --> 00:52:07,530
给你这个
Take this.

937
00:52:26,760 --> 00:52:28,220
很好
Oh, this is good.

938
00:52:28,300 --> 00:52:29,390
车明集团千永裴因手推车佳话 在社交媒体上引起了热议
HOT ON SOCIAL MEDIA, FEEL-GOOD STORY WITH CHEON YEONGBAE

939
00:52:29,470 --> 00:52:31,310
这样的形象也不错
This isn't bad at all.

940
00:52:31,850 --> 00:52:34,560
没错 贵族义务
That's right, "Noblesse Oblige."

941
00:52:34,850 --> 00:52:36,690
不错嘛
This is great.

942
00:52:36,770 --> 00:52:38,860
我对车明集团改变看法了
I VIEW THE CHAMYEONG GROUP DIFFERENTLY NOW

943
00:52:38,940 --> 00:52:40,070
让我想想
Let's see.

944
00:52:40,730 --> 00:52:43,110
我以后得活得善良点吗
Do I have to be good from now on? Hmm?

945
00:52:44,450 --> 00:52:47,320
不可能 凭什么
No way. Why should I?

946
00:52:49,870 --> 00:52:50,700
等一下
Wait.

947
00:52:50,780 --> 00:52:52,290
会长的庭审
THE CHAIRMAN'S TRIAL

948
00:52:52,870 --> 00:52:54,250
喂 尹秘书
Secretary Yoon!

949
00:52:54,750 --> 00:52:56,000
是
Yes, sir?

950
00:52:56,080 --> 00:52:57,170
喂
Hey.

951
00:52:57,960 --> 00:53:00,500
你为什么不告诉我 今天是毛会长开庭的日子
Why didn't you tell me today was the chairman's trial?

952
00:53:00,630 --> 00:53:03,090
他不让任何人去 因为这样显得不好
He didn't want anyone to come because it didn't look good.

953
00:53:03,170 --> 00:53:06,050
该死 那你也应该告诉我
Damn it! You still should have told me!

954
00:53:06,930 --> 00:53:09,720
可恶 我要疯了
Geez. I'm freaking out.

955
00:53:22,440 --> 00:53:24,240
庭审中发生了什么
What happened at the trial?

956
00:53:24,820 --> 00:53:26,530
