Chairman, I'm sorry I'm late.

960
00:53:44,000 --> 00:53:45,050
你受苦了
You must have suffered.

961
00:53:48,470 --> 00:53:51,140
你没有忘记我千永裴啊
You haven't forgotten Cheon Yeongbae.

962
00:53:51,220 --> 00:53:54,270
我怎么能忘记你呢 我们的关系可不一般
How can I forget you? We have such a special history.

963
00:53:54,850 --> 00:53:57,850
不过你的声音…
But... your voice is...

964
00:54:04,730 --> 00:54:05,730
你这家伙…
Why you jerk...

965
00:54:06,320 --> 00:54:08,150
你怎么会在这里
What are you doing here? Huh?

966
00:54:08,780 --> 00:54:09,860
喂
Hey.

967
00:54:11,370 --> 00:54:12,830
他是我的律师
He's my lawyer.

968
00:54:14,030 --> 00:54:15,790
律师？
Law... Lawyer?

969
00:54:15,950 --> 00:54:18,870
毛会长不让你们来 你还是来了
The chairman said not to come, but you are here.

970
00:54:18,960 --> 00:54:21,710
你还真是一片赤心啊
You are such a loyal employee. Hmm.

971
00:54:21,790 --> 00:54:22,630
我们要不要一起走
Shall we go together?

972
00:54:22,710 --> 00:54:25,340
一起走？要去哪里
Together? Where to?

973
