辛苦了 千律师 不愧是你
Good job. Mr. Cheon is the best.

980
00:54:48,820 --> 00:54:50,200
我倒是不辛苦
It wasn't that hard.

981
00:54:50,740 --> 00:54:53,990
你要是再犯 我绝不会手下留情
If you do it one more time, I will take you down.

982
00:54:54,580 --> 00:54:56,830
你活得善良点吧 老头
Be a good person, old man.

983
00:54:57,870 --> 00:54:59,160
老头？
Old man?

984
00:54:59,250 --> 00:55:01,330
你知道我因为这次的事损失了多少吧
Do you know how much I lost because of this?

985
00:55:01,420 --> 00:55:03,830
司机 掉头 我们得把车开回去
Driver, do a U-turn. We have to turn the car around.

986
00:55:03,920 --> 00:55:05,130
他还没有悔过自新
I don't think he gets it.

987
00:55:05,210 --> 00:55:06,590
别掉头 算了
No, no. I get it.

988
00:55:07,170 --> 00:55:09,420
我又不能把那笔钱带进坟墓
It's not like I can take that money to my grave with me.

989
00:55:10,300 --> 00:55:13,340
对啊 你这样想就对了
You're right. That's a good way to think about it.

990
00:55:14,890 --> 00:55:19,350
不过你们是怎么认识的
So... how do you two know each other?

991
00:55:19,430 --> 00:55:21,690
你为什么突然对我说敬语
Why are you so polite all of a sudden?

992
00:55:21,770 --> 00:55:23,100
你之前还叫我家伙
You used to call me a bastard.

993
00:55:23,690 --> 00:55:24,980
我什么时候这么叫过你
When did I do that?

994
00:55:25,060 --> 00:55:26,320
你干吗提这个
What are you saying?

995
00:55:27,270 --> 00:55:28,940
你们两个认识吗
Do you two know each other?

996
00:55:29,900 --> 00:55:32,950
-那个… -对 我们很熟
-Well... -Yes. We know each other well.

997
00:55:33,030 --> 00:55:34,070
怎么认识的
How?

998
00:55:35,740 --> 00:55:38,450
让千永裴专务来说一下 我们是什么关系吧
Executive Director Cheon, why don't you tell him how we know each other?

999
00:55:38,540 --> 00:55:40,580
好 那个…
Yes, well...

1000
00:55:40,660 --> 00:55:42,460
在某一天
So, one day,

1001
00:55:45,210 --> 00:55:48,300
该怎么说呢 很美好…
What can I say, it was kind of beautiful...

1002
00:55:48,380 --> 00:55:50,050
你在跟我闹着玩吗
Hey, are you joking?

1003
00:55:50,170 --> 00:55:51,840
你干什么啊 放开我
What are you doing? Let go of me!

1004
00:55:52,420 --> 00:55:55,090
我们之间本就没有隔阂
We did away with formalities.

1005
00:55:55,180 --> 00:55:56,180
你这个疯子
You wacko.

1006
00:55:56,260 --> 00:55:57,300
别在我面前嚣张
Don't mess with me, damn it!

1007
00:55:57,640 --> 00:55:59,220
你这个疯子
You crazy scumbag!

1008
00:56:00,430 --> 00:56:02,100
我们真心为彼此着想
We truly care about each other.

1009
00:56:02,180 --> 00:56:04,140
还有什么 你继续说
What else? Keep going.

1010
00:56:04,230 --> 00:56:09,190
好 我们无论是商业上还是私下 都是很理想的关系
Yes. we have an ideal relationship as business partners and friends.

1011
00:56:09,980 --> 00:56:11,240
对吧
Isn't that right?

1012
00:56:11,820 --> 00:56:14,360
就这些啊 我们走着瞧就知道了
That must be it. We'll see.

1013
00:56:14,860 --> 00:56:16,530
你中午想吃什么
What would you like for lunch?

1014
00:56:17,530 --> 00:56:19,790
干炸酱面怎么样 再加盘煎饺
Perhaps we can order jjajangmyeon with a side of dumplings?

1015
00:56:20,330 --> 00:56:21,830
点一样就行
Just order one.

1016
00:56:30,340 --> 00:56:31,300
这些人都是谁
Who are all these people?

1017
00:56:31,380 --> 00:56:33,550
毛会长 他们是车明建设的员工
Chairman, these are employees of Chamyeong Construction.

1018
00:56:34,760 --> 00:56:37,430
那不是你负责的地方吗 又出什么问题了
Isn't this your responsibility? What is the problem again?

1019
00:56:37,510 --> 00:56:40,180
哪有什么问题 他们总是这样
There is no problem. They always do this.

1020
00:56:40,260 --> 00:56:42,020
我让他们回去
I will send them away.

1021
00:56:42,180 --> 00:56:43,480
这些家伙 该死的
Those morons. Damn it.

1022
00:56:44,180 --> 00:56:45,480
毛会长 等一下
Hold on, Chairman.

1023
00:56:47,230 --> 00:56:48,270
我说
Wait a minute.

1024
00:56:49,400 --> 00:56:51,190
你们这些人
You people!

1025
00:56:52,030 --> 00:56:54,280
你们当这是什么地方
Where do you think this is?

1026
00:57:04,250 --> 00:57:05,460
你们来得正好
Welcome.

1027
00:57:10,590 --> 00:57:13,300
毛会长 他们是我的委托人
Chairman, these are my clients.

1028
00:57:16,130 --> 00:57:17,430
你这是在干什么
What are you doing?

1029
00:57:19,510 --> 00:57:20,720
我们打算起诉你
We are about to sue you.

1030
00:57:21,310 --> 00:57:23,850
什么 又有谁要起诉我
What? Who's suing me now?

1031
00:57:24,350 --> 00:57:28,190
我按照你说的 已经对上次的事给予补偿了
I compensated for the last incident just as you told me to.

1032
00:57:28,270 --> 00:57:31,360
你又对眼前这些人犯错了
You did these people wrong again.

1033
00:57:31,440 --> 00:57:32,610
我什么时候
When did I do that?

1034
00:57:32,820 --> 00:57:36,320
严格来说 这不是你亲自所为
Technically speaking, you didn't do it personally.

1035
00:57:36,400 --> 00:57:38,360
