But one of your deputies,

1036
00:57:40,070 --> 00:57:41,950
千永裴专务干的
Executive Director Cheon Yeongbae did.

1037
00:57:43,990 --> 00:57:45,830
你这混…
You jerk--

1038
00:57:46,830 --> 00:57:49,670
-不是那样的… -闭嘴 安静点
-What happened was-- -Shut up. Be quiet.

1039
00:57:50,290 --> 00:57:52,250
我不在的时候你都做了什么
What have you done while I was gone?

1040
00:57:52,880 --> 00:57:54,050
对不起
I'm sorry.

1041
00:57:54,420 --> 00:57:57,220
千律师 你想要什么
Mr. Cheon, what do you want?

1042
00:57:57,720 --> 00:57:59,430
向他们郑重道歉 并给予合理的补偿
A sincere apology, a just compensation,

1043
00:57:59,510 --> 00:58:02,470
