and preventative measures to ensure it doesn't happen again.

1044
00:58:02,970 --> 00:58:05,140
又不是我干的 你却让我补偿他们
Do I have to pay for something I didn't do?

1045
00:58:05,220 --> 00:58:07,640
对 我完全理解你
Yes. I completely understand.

1046
00:58:08,230 --> 00:58:10,400
这不是你干的
This is not something you did personally.

1047
00:58:10,480 --> 00:58:15,230
