什么
What?

1052
00:58:27,660 --> 00:58:29,120
宾果游戏？
Bingo?

1053
00:58:29,210 --> 00:58:30,540
如果我输了
If I lose,

1054
00:58:31,000 --> 00:58:34,630
我们就撤回所有要求 干脆利落地走人
we will withdraw all of our demands and leave.

1055
00:58:34,840 --> 00:58:36,300
但如果我赢了
But if I win,

1056
00:58:36,380 --> 00:58:39,420
你就必须满足他们的所有要求
you must meet all of their demands and at the same time,

1057
00:58:40,760 --> 00:58:43,140
同时我们要求千永裴专务…
we demand Executive Director Cheon Yeongbae...

1058
