1063
00:58:55,730 --> 00:58:57,730
你疯了 你是不是疯了
You're crazy. Are you crazy?

1064
00:58:58,740 --> 00:59:01,530
-怎么了 -宾果游戏？这像话吗
-Why? -Bingo? Does that make any sense?

1065
00:59:04,620 --> 00:59:07,450
你说他是替委托人战斗的律师
You said he fights in his client's stead.

1066
00:59:08,160 --> 00:59:10,960
还说这是他的理念
You said that was this lawyer's philosophy.

1067
00:59:11,040 --> 00:59:14,210
替委托人战斗确实是我的理念
Fighting for the client is my philosophy. That is correct.

1068
