You have to decide carefully whether it's a civil or a criminal case.

1072
00:59:25,550 --> 00:59:26,760
还是刑事案件后 就去战斗啊
You have to decide carefully whether it's a civil or a criminal case.

1073
00:59:26,850 --> 00:59:27,930
还是刑事案件后 就去战斗啊
Then fight it out.

1074
00:59:28,100 --> 00:59:30,350
如果我们去战斗 总有一天会赢
We may eventually win if we fight.

1075
00:59:30,430 --> 00:59:33,520
可那一天具体是什么时候呢
But when exactly is that?

1076
00:59:33,600 --> 00:59:34,690
什么
What?

1077
00:59:34,770 --> 00:59:37,270
他们会更换律师 并以各种借口进行二审
They will change lawyers and make excuses to go to second trial,

1078
00:59:37,360 --> 00:59:39,280
这样又会浪费几个月
wasting a few months.

1079
00:59:39,360 --> 00:59:43,530
那在这期间 这里的职员都在做什么呢
What will these people be doing in the meantime?

1080
00:59:44,240 --> 00:59:45,700
他们应该在上班吧
They will be working at this company.

1081
00:59:45,780 --> 00:59:47,700
在谁的手底下呢
Under who?

1082
00:59:49,240 --> 00:59:51,500
就在千永裴专务的手底下
Under Executive Director Cheon Yeongbae.

1083
00:59:54,170 --> 00:59:57,210
可是如果你输了游戏怎么办
But what if you lose the game?

1084
00:59:58,670 --> 01:00:01,380
你把这么重要的事情交给运气吗
Why would you leave something this important to luck?

1085
01:00:03,550 --> 01:00:06,430
如果我看人的眼光没错的话 那就不是靠运气
