01:12:48,980 --> 01:12:50,940
我希望你们可以负责一个案件
I hope you can take this case.

1278
01:12:51,030 --> 01:12:52,280
这是凶杀案
It's a murder case.

1279
01:12:52,780 --> 01:12:54,400
你接这种案件想干什么啊
What are you taking this case for?

1280
01:12:54,610 --> 01:12:55,820
他杀了自己的父母啊
He killed his parents.

1281
01:12:56,030 --> 01:12:57,120
前所未闻的恶魔
The devil of the ages.

1282
01:12:57,200 --> 01:12:58,780
我听说你主张自己无罪
I heard you claim innocence.

1283
01:12:58,870 --> 01:13:01,120
你的双亲去世了 你不难过吗
Both of your parents died. Aren't you sad?

1284
01:13:01,200 --> 01:13:02,250
我一定要难过吗
Do I have to be sad?

1285
01:13:02,330 --> 01:13:04,500
千智勋接了这起案件 你来负责吧
Cheon Jihun took this case. I want you to be in charge.

1286
01:13:04,580 --> 01:13:06,420
我要亲眼看看犯罪现场
I need to see the crime scene in person.

1287
01:13:06,580 --> 01:13:07,920
你真的相信他还活着吗
Do you really believe he's alive?

1288
01:13:08,000 --> 01:13:09,500
应该还活着躲在某个地方
They are alive and probably hiding somewhere.

1289
01:13:09,790 --> 01:13:11,460
千律师 外面有人
Mr. Cheon, someone is out there!